# Todo List Day Planner App

## Core Functionality
1. Task Management
   - Add, edit, and delete tasks
   - Set due dates and priorities
   - Mark tasks as complete

2. Day Planning
   - View tasks organized by day
   - Drag and drop to reorder tasks
   - Set reminders for important tasks

3. Analytics Dashboard

#Additional Functionality
6. Simple Notes
   - Add quick notes or thoughts
   - Attach notes to specific days or tasks

7. Time Capsule
   - Write notes or upload photos for future dates
   - Receive notifications when time capsules "open"

8. Settings
   - Customize notifications
   - Choose app theme
   - Backup and sync data

## Potential Future Expansions
- Collaboration features (shared lists)
- Integration with calendar apps
- More detailed analytics and insights
